notesStmt.note: Several items are attributed to Manuel Valades y Leon in headings.
Two printed items laid in, a bookmark and a holy card depicting the Blessed Virgin Mary.

msContents.summary: Astrological texts illustrated with numerous diagrams, tables, and pen and ink drawings; with some material on navigation, the astrolabe and quadrant.

supportDesc.extent: 212 leaves : 155 x 110 mm. bound to 159 x 109 mm
supportDesc.foliation: Paper, 212 + i; [i], 1-37, 1-25, 1-10, [lxxvi], 1-49, [i], 1-10, 13, [ii], contemporary foliation in ink, upper right recto; [1-212], modern foliation in pencil, upper right recto.

decoDesc.decoNote: Illustrated with diagrams, tables, symbols of the zodiac, calendars, and pen and ink drawings.

binding.p: Contemporary boards. Upper cover detached; lower cover nearly detached.
